Brief: INFORMATION: Suede upper, suede sole. The original barefoot shoe from Capezio is a great contemporary shoe that gives the look of a bare foot. In tone on tone, this shoe is an excellent match to your skin tone, creating a perfect legline. The thong shaped suede upper fits between the big toe and the second toe, with the half-sole covering the ball of the foot for protection during turns. The short elastic straps help the shoe hug the foot for a secure fit and feel. Ideal for belly and modern dancing. Made in Thailand. Original Capezio dance product. Product: Veronese II -- Pointe Shoe -- European Pink Satin
Brief: INFORMATION: Satin Upper, leather sole. The Chacott Veronese II model is one of the lightest weight pointe shoes on the market today. Lightweight pointe shoes are preferred by dancers who make comfort and ease of break in a number one priority. The design of the Veronese II wingless toe box makes this an ideal pointe shoe for dancers with painful bunions. To compensate for the wingless box, Chacott designed the vamp of the Veronese II to fit snugly over the toes the way that many lower profile pointe shoes fit. This snug fit gives additional support to the foot while on pointe. The vamp on the Veronese II is shorter and well suited for short toes that taper. The vamp also has a modified v-shape that allows for ease of roll through.

Brief: INFORMATION: Rubin (Russian for "ruby") has a wide toe platform and low crown. This model has a pre-arched shape that mimics the shape of the foot on pointe, enhancing longevity while minimizing break-in. Dancers with high arches will experience decreased pressure on the front of the foot. Dancers with very low arches will find it easier to reach full pointe. Sleek and elegant pleatless toe platform eliminates fringing, improves balance, and enhances the appearance of the dancer’s elegant foot lines. Made in Russia. * Original Russian Pointe dance product.

Product: Pro Elastic Canvas -- Split Sole Ballet -- Black
Brief: INFORMATION: Canvas Upper, suede forefoot and heel. The Pro Elastic was developed for interdisciplinary work: ballet, gymnastics, lyrical, and jazz. It has an upper that has an upper like a ballet flat but in place of a binding and drawstring, it has an elastic piece that contours to the foot in a full range of movement. This soft elastic is ideal for floor work where the top of the foot is in contact with the floor, eliminating bruising from pressure where the drawstring is knotted. This triangular stretch canvas split sole ballet has a 100% cotton lining, pre-sewn elastics, and a forefoot outsole pad that is shaped to protect the metatarsals and minimize bulk in the arch when pointing. Made in Thailand. Original Bloch dance product.

Product: Pro Elastic Canvas -- Split Sole Ballet -- Pink
Brief: INFORMATION: Canvas Upper, suede forefoot and heel. The Pro Elastic was developed for interdisciplinary work: ballet, gymnastics, lyrical, and jazz. It has an upper that has an upper like a ballet flat but in place of a binding and drawstring, it has an elastic piece that contours to the foot in a full range of movement. This soft elastic is ideal for floor work where the top of the foot is in contact with the floor, eliminating bruising from pressure where the drawstring is knotted. This triangular stretch canvas split sole ballet has a 100% cotton lining, pre-sewn elastics, and a forefoot outsole pad that is shaped to protect the metatarsals and minimise bulk in the arch when pointing. Made in Thailand. Original Bloch dance product.

Product: Love Ballet -- Full Sole Ballet -- Ballet Pink
Brief: INFORMATION: Leather upper, suede sole. Grows with Me! Love Ballet is designed and engineered to grow with the child and give them an updated look with a more mature feel Soft, comfortable, adjustable & fun! Soft leather upper with a power mesh Growth Pocket , soft elastic binding and adjustable instep straps all work together so every child can learn to love ballet. Adjustable Instep Strap System features a plush elastic strap with a heart shaped button on each end. Find the most comfortable placement, place the button through the bottom holes on the elastic. It will stay buttoned and in place until you need to change it! As the child grows, adjust the strap for fit and comfort. Hybrid Sole Design features a two part suede sole that allows the shoe to function as both a full sole and a split sole. The forepart extends long enough to work like a full sole and help young feet strengthen. The gap allows for the Growth Pocket; to stretch and the heel cup has extended coverage for comfort and stability. Flirty print cotton lining featuring hearts, flowers, butterflies and lady bugs. Lightly padded insole and cotton socklining, No Drawstring.
